fields.name: Step 4 | The Great Fight Against The Dragon
fields.content_text: You fight the great Smaug Dragon in the mountain. It's epic !

fields.name: Step 5 | The Treasure Is Here
fields.content_text: You won the fight and found the treasure. You are the world savior. Good Job man.

fields.name: Step 3 | A Long Road
fields.content_text:
You walk for days and days in dangerous forests and fields. You face monsters every day and cross the river of Anduin.

You are now in front of the dangerous mountain of Smaug !

fields.name: Step 2 | The Giant Bear
fields.content_text:
You face a group of dangerous bats. You hear a weird noise in the darkness...

Oh Oh...

You are facing a giant bear !

fields.name: Step 1 | Enter The Cave
fields.content_text: There is a cave in front of you, you have to enter to continue the journey. Don't be scared !
